chrisgit:org:open.description: Modified version of force:org:open to allow you to specify the browser
examples: $ Single browser                   ->  sfdx chrisgit:org:open -u scratchOrg -b iexplore
$ Single browser developer console ->  sfdx chrisgit:org:open -u scratchOrg -b iexplore --devconsole
$ Multiple browsers                ->  sfdx chrisgit:org:open -u scratchOrg -b "firefox, edge, chrome"
$ Multiple browsers                ->  sfdx chrisgit:org:open -u scratchOrg -b firefox,edge,chrome

loglevel.name: loglevel
